{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/demo.png?t=1727661173\" />This demo gives unlimited access to the first area of the game, and all progress made in the demo transfers to the full version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After being deployed into enemy territory for the first time, your unit is ambushed and you become a prisoner of war. Until you break out of prison, carving a path of destruction on your way back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/inf_mode_1.gif?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/infinite_mode.png?t=1727661173\" />Fight against endless hordes of enemies and try to obtain a high score in the wave-based Infinite Mode! Choose from one of 4 demo maps and customize your experience with more than the 50 available game-play modifiers or play one of 15 challenge modes. Unlock dozens of cosmetics and achievements for reaching score and wave milestones, all of which will carry over into the full game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/inf_mode_shop.gif?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/story_mode.png?t=1727661173\" />Play through the beginning of the level-based story mode and follow the Clippy Commando's adventure as you save the Clipenberg Empire from the threat of the Rulerian Alliance! Each level has a variety of unique optional objectives that offer anything from unique dialogue between the Clippy Commando and fellow war criminal Quartermaster Unicorn to unlocking one of a dozen cosmetics, all of which carry over into the full game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/dialogue.gif?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/coop.png?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play Infinite Mode with up to 4 players... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/inf_mode_multiplayer_1_short.gif?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/pvp.png?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">... or fight to the death in Deathmatch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/deathmatch.gif?t=1727661173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141450/extras/features.png?t=1727661173\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 Weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 Infinite Mode maps, each with unique game-play elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15 Infinite Mode challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20 Story Mode levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">50 Customizable Infinite Mode game-play modifiers to tailor your experience</p></li><li><p clas